metadata.title: Lazy AI: Revolutionizing Web Development with Claude's AI-Powered Code Generation \ Anthropic
metadata.description: Discover how Lazy AI leverages Anthropic's Claude to democratize web development, reducing code fixes by 51% and achieving a 73% success rate in first-attempt feature implementation. Learn how this AI-driven platform is transforming the software creation landscape for developers and businesses alike.
